<P ALIGN="CENTER"><FONT SIZE="-1" COLOR="GREEN"><I>Rig Veda</I>, tr. by Ralph T.H. Griffith, [1896], at sacred-texts.com</FONT></P><HR></p>  <h3 align="center" align="center">HYMN XCIX. Agni.</h3>  
<p>1. FOR J&#257;tavedas let us press the Soma: may he consume the wealth of the malignant.<br> May Agni carry us through all our troubles, through grief as in a boat across the river.</p>  
